                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "After completing the reasoning in Heterogeneous Tree Structures, the aggregation process of BoT first extracts the best reasoning chain from each tree and then combines them using either the Best- First or Greedy aggregation method into a single reasoning chain. More details of these two aggregation methods can be accessed in the source code examples/BoostingOfThought/BoT Aggregation."
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ],
                    "index": 4
